Docs.summary: A Class representing the complex channel for UWB which comprises channel and preamble index negotiated between peer devices out of band before ranging.

remarks.para: A Class representing the complex channel for UWB which comprises channel and preamble index negotiated between peer devices out of band before ranging.

PRF (Pulse Repetition Frequency) supported:
  • BPRF - Base Pulse Repetition Frequency.
  • HPRF - Higher Pulse Repetition Frequency.
See FiRa UCI Spec.
